From: linuxram@us.ibm.com (Ram Pai)
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
X-Mailing-List: linux-kernel@vger.kernel.org

This optional patch, provides the ability to identify the export-type of each
of the exported symbols, in the report generated by 'make export_report'

This patch also updates the Module.symvers file with the additional information
as shown below.

0x0f8b92af      platform_device_add_resources   vmlinux EXPORT_GPL_ONLY
0xcf7efb2a      ethtool_op_set_tx_csum          vmlinux EXPORT_ALL


Signed-off-by Ram Pai (linuxram@us.ibm.com)
Signed-off-by Avantika Mathur (mathur@us.ibm.com)

